OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start for many with
OL,6,Fsome cloud around. Otherwise a dry day
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine developing.
OL,8,FFeeling quite warm in the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry night with long clear spells.
OL,13,FBecoming chilly overnight with a touch
OL,14,Fof frost in places and patchy fog.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother dry and bright day
OL,17,Fwith long periods of sunshine. A
OL,18,Fchilly start then becoming quite warm
OL,19,Finland by the afternoon but cooler
OL,20,Falong the coast with patchy mist.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
