OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Saturday but rather cool and
OL,7,Fcloudy. A lot of dry and bright
OL,8,Fweather on Sunday and Monday and
OL,9,Fturning a little warmer again.
